title: Schoolhouse Rock - Math Rock
description:
Schoolhouse Rock is probably the most popular and useful educational video series, ever.

In this case, we have Math Rock, music videos about each of the numbers up to 12, including an explanation of our base-10 math system...somehow each made more fun than even the most pointless kid's cartoon.


Face it, you learned more about certain things from Schoolhouse Rock than you ever did from public school...and now your kids can, too!

Music by Bob Dorough, Grady Tate, Blossom Dearie, Lynn Ahrens, Jack Sheldon, and others.

This version of the torrent is now working correctly...it had clashed with an old copy, previously.
